Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Tapulang Elementary School in Barangay Tapulang, in the Municipality of Maayon, Province of Capiz, to Don Mariano Marcos Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 833
An Act Changing the Name of the Tapulang Elementary School in Barangay Tapulang, in the Municipality of Maayon, Province of Capiz, to Don Mariano Marcos Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Tapulang Elementary School in Barangay Tapulang, Municipality of Maayon, Province of Capiz, is changed to Don Mariano Marcos Memorial School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
